gmd:title.gco:CharacterString: Noise data reported under Environmental Noise Directive (END)

gmd:abstract.gco:CharacterString: The datasets includes 1) the noise exposure data, 2) the noise contours data, 3) razterized noise contours data and 4) potential quiet areas all under the terms of the Environmental Noise Directive (END). Data covers the EEA32 member countries and the United Kingdom (excluding Turkey for the third round of noise mapping in 2017).
